{
  "stem": "2916.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But when she didn't have a wig on, she had her hair covered completely.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I already visualized her face without hair.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But she didn't recognize me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so she-- she was looking for me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then she said, oh, Bubbe.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Suddenly, she thought I was my brother, because I looked like a boy with my hair gone.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "From this point, we were driven into another part of this building and another.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the doors closed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And from the ceiling, water started rushing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And this was the so-called shower.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Cold water rushed on us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then from there, again, we were driven out into the third part of this building where there were grey, like, sack-like straight dresses, which didn't have any sleeves or anything else.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It was just a grey piece with the holes for arms and the hole for your head.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we had to put that on.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And somebody with a large paint-- with red paintbrush painted on the back a K and an L, which stood for [NON-ENGLISH], which was concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And, again, we were driven out and lined up by fives.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "This was the first roll call, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And from this roll call, again, we were marched.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And then we were marched into the camp itself.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We were driven into barracks.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "The barracks in this place-- later, I found out that this was a part of Auschwitz called Birkenau, which was rather new.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And the barracks were not built yet completely.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So there was-- would be a wooden structure only with doors and windows not completed.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was just like a skeleton of a-- of a structure.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so we-- we were driven there.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
